'''Minna Kaisa Aaltonen''' (born 17 September 1966; [[Turku]]) is a [[Finland|Finnish]] actress. She played Marianne in ''[[London's Burning (TV series)|London's Burning]]'', Ingrid Coates in ''[[Dream Team (TV series)|Dream Team]]'', and appeared in ''[[Kotikatu]]'', ''[[The Bill]]'', ''[[Dalziel and Pascoe (TV series)|Dalziel and Pascoe]]'', and ''[[Lexx]]''. She also appeared in [[beer]] ads in [[Ireland]]<ref name="imdb.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0007392/|title=Minna Aaltonen|website=[[IMDb]]|accessdate=26 March 2018}}</ref> and in a small part as a newsreader in the [[James Bond]] movie ''[[Tomorrow Never Dies]]''.<ref name="imdb.com"/> In 1994 she was a host of [[Gladiaattorit]] (Finnish Gladiators).<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.helsinginuutiset.fi/artikkeli/482097-muistathan-gladiaattoreiden-salaman-talta-marjo-krishi-nayttaa-nyt-muistelee-tony|title=Muistathan Gladiaattoreiden Salaman? Tältä Marjo Krishi näyttää nyt – muistelee Tony "Viikinki" Halmetta lämmöllä|language=Finnish|date=2 February 2017|accessdate=26 March 2018}}</ref>

